<p>Hey there Junkies!  This one's for you . Get all your junk together and lets get creative.<br/><br/>
This event lets you create your own working models, machines etc., for destroying targets, from waste materials. Each team consists of five members. With the provided waste materials and tools, the team will have to build their model within a time frame that will be suggested by the team itself. Each junk material has its own points and depending on the team's selection of materials, points will be granted.
</p>